          <answer>
            <p><m>\sin\frac{\pi}{2}=1</m>; <m>\cos\frac{\pi}{2}=0</m>; <m>\tan\frac{\pi}{2}</m> is undefined; <m>\csc\frac{\pi}{2}=1</m>; <m>\sec\frac{\pi}{2}</m> is undefined; <m>\cot\frac{\pi}{2}=0</m></p>
          </answer>
        </exercise>
        <exercise>
