            <p><m>\sin\frac{5\pi}{6}=\frac{1}{2}</m>; <m>\cos\frac{5\pi}{6}=-\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}</m>; <m>\tan\frac{5\pi}{6}=-\frac{\sqrt{3}}{3}</m>; <m>\csc\frac{5\pi}{6}=2</m>; <m>\sec\frac{5\pi}{6}=-\frac{2\sqrt{3}}{3}</m>; <m>\cot\frac{5\pi}{6}=-\sqrt{3}</m></p>
          </answer>
        </exercise>
        <exercise>
